longBusinessSummary: Ensurge, Inc. engages in the exploration, development, and evaluation of mining properties. It explores for gold and diamond. The company was formerly known as iShopper.com, Inc. and changed its name to Ensurge, Inc. in October 2000. Ensurge, Inc. was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Folsom, California.
